    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "IN FLIGHT WITH\nUNITED AIR LINES\nPOWER, STAMINA, SPEED -\nEquipped\nwith new geared Wasps\nand three-bladed controllable pro-\npellers,\nthis new Boeing 247-D of\nUnited Air Lines has a cruising speed of 189 mph, a\ntop of 202 mph. It can fly and even climb, fully loaded,\non only one of its 550 h.p. supercharged Wasp engines.\nPOST CARD\nPlease address\nand return to\nstewardess who\nwill stamp and\nmail card\nfor you."
    ],
